{"tid":582643,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"不要暗戀，去強姦。– – –哥布林","createTime":"2018-03-06T10:54:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-09T06:44:04.000Z","uid":13138,"like":187,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"b234ef2a102bc83724e0c3928f74db24edc1be9c","tid":582643,"uid":13138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T10:54:26.000Z","msg":"不要暗戀，去強姦。人生沒有那麼多時間給你演內心戲。愛她就去搞她，喜歡就去強姦。表白有什麼用還是會被拒絕。追不到就下藥，翻臉就殺了她。大不了就被殺，你連投胎都不敢還好意思說愛她。投胎長大之後找到她繼續強姦，強姦到讓她開始懷疑自己的人生，讓她覺得她人生的意義就是被你強姦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&ndash; &ndash; &ndash;哥布林<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/03/06/QUXNTb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F03%2F06%2FQUXNTb.jpg&h=9e5dc3fc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"06efdd0ce16ed40ac6ad4b2dffb12109928cfadc","tid":582643,"uid":13138,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T11:00:07.000Z","msg":"我地哥布林係唔驚死架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"548004339dbf9f424f6ce990403a07bae5efc5c4","tid":582643,"uid":8307,"like":13,"dislike":12,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T11:03:21.000Z","msg":"叫雞又冇錢,cow女又cow唔到<br />\n想屌閪,就緊係去強姦..."},{"pid":"899d049f91090b81d5fabc17dce2d361d32ad316","tid":582643,"uid":6327,"like":127,"dislike":1,"score":126,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T11:05:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/06/190514_c434a6d34804d88c26b56af8a07b1673.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F06%2F190514_c434a6d34804d88c26b56af8a07b1673.png&h=64a70796&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8873f2ed9473824e242b5ed7e352986c0d34baa8","tid":582643,"uid":76364,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"548004339dbf9f424f6ce990403a07bae5efc5c4","tid":582643,"uid":8307,"like":13,"dislike":12,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T11:03:21.000Z